ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩幫到樓主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"我已經睇臨床心理同精神科<br />\n都係開血清我食<br />\n<br />\n但其實食完個自殺衝動仲大咗<br />\n<br />\n係搵到D嘢禁住自己唔好俾自己亂嚟"},{"pid":"6490395acc48aaf357c833ab2609b112319caa71","tid":1292552,"uid":106954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"搵啲fd出下街 食下野<br />\n將你啲唔開心嘅野 同佢地傾訴下"},{"pid":"cc7cb6aa9d9dda2a9e481d4b492e3f0067fdfdb6","tid":1292552,"uid":93314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6490395acc48aaf357c833ab2609b112319caa71","tid":1292552,"uid":106954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"搵啲fd出下街 食下野<br />\n將你啲唔開心嘅野 同佢地傾訴下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"都唔知點講<br />\n自己已經負到好緊要<br />\n會唔會累咗人<br />\n<br />\n而且自己的問題係覺得自己好廢好無用<br />\n過唔到自己個關"},{"pid":"d26ba28eba2208e9f709ea21a67ca0aa1544c157","tid":1292552,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65700ea736733dc546c159436cd10d636343ccde","tid":1292552,"uid":93314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cdca7bf12b9ef615c9e29c80ae1362b86e875e7e","tid":1292552,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25573f3553e66c8db6c138a09443a991f8e52d7","tid":1292552,"uid":93314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"其實我已經捱唔住了<br />\n<br />\n之前有個種「死」的覺悟向前衝<br />\n最後就俾人抬返出嚟..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩幫到樓主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"我已經睇臨床心理同精神科<br />\n都係開血清我食<br />\n<br />\n但其實食完個自殺衝動仲大咗<br />\n<br />\n係搵到D嘢禁住自己唔好俾自己亂嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"係咪搵到令自己舒服啲嘅方法/pattern <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98961026bf5ca71f0e289449217c0869ce04a33f","tid":1292552,"uid":9